   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_1_00004"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place">Ischl</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb766" type="place">Egelmoos 22</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_1_00006"/><salute>Lieber Richard.</salute> Meine Ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>icht i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t es,
                  <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time> abzurei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en. Ich bin dann <time>7 Uhr früh</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date> in <rs ref="#pmb45258" type="place">München</rs>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>teige <rs ref="#pmb199" type="place">Hotel <hi rend="latintype">Maximilian</hi></rs> ab. Bitte um Nachricht, was Sie thun. –</p><p>Hab von <rs ref="#pmb10992" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Brandes</hi></rs> einen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chönen Brief über’s <rs ref="#pmb29823" type="work">Märchen</rs> beko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en. – Heut einen <pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_1_00007"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>echs
               Seiten langen noch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chönern über alle möglichen Sachen von der <rs ref="#pmb10762" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Lou Salomé</hi></rs>.</p><closer>Herzlichen Gru<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s. Ich freue mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr, ein paar Tage mit Ihnen zu
                  verbringen.<lb/>Ihr<signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
